# LDM — Phase One Development Path  
## Transition from Phase Zero Concept → Validated Engineering Prototype

_Last Updated: Phase One Draft_

Phase One transforms the **Lunar Dust Mitigator (LDM)** from a credible physics concept into a **measured, test-backed subsystem** suitable for consideration as a future lunar surface demo.

Phase Zero answered:  
> “Does this architecture make sense?”

Phase One answers:  
> “Does it actually work, and does it survive long enough to matter?”

The purpose of Phase One is **evidence**, not flight hardware.

---

